[
  {
    "text": "- Let me get this straight.",
    "start": 2.234,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "You two ordered a giant screen\ntelevision",
    "start": 3.702,
    "duration": 2.837
  },
  {
    "text": "just so you could play in the\nbox?",
    "start": 6.572,
    "duration": 2.703
  },
  {
    "text": "- Pretty smart, huh?",
    "start": 9.308,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "- I thought it wouldn't work.",
    "start": 10.309,
    "duration": 1.202
  },
  {
    "text": "- Yeah, that's quite a plan\nthere.",
    "start": 11.544,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, but wait,",
    "start": 13.245,
    "duration": 1.269
  },
  {
    "text": "there's something else\nI wanted to ask you two.",
    "start": 14.547,
    "duration": 2.936
  },
  {
    "text": "What was it?",
    "start": 17.516,
    "duration": 1.702
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh yeah, yeah.",
    "start": 19.251,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't you two have any brains?",
    "start": 20.619,
    "duration": 2.703
  },
  {
    "text": "- Squidward, we don't need\ntelevision.",
    "start": 23.355,
    "duration": 3.037
  },
  {
    "text": "Not as long as we have our\nimagination.",
    "start": 26.425,
    "duration": 3.338
  },
  {
    "text": "- Okay, let's see.",
    "start": 32.531,
    "duration": 1.536
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm imagining myself watching\nTV.",
    "start": 34.1,
    "duration": 3.07
  },
  {
    "text": "And there it is!",
    "start": 37.203,
    "duration": 1.468
  },
  {
    "text": "Can I have it, Spongebob?",
    "start": 38.704,
    "duration": 1.001
  },
  {
    "text": "- Sure, Squidward.",
    "start": 39.738,
    "duration": 0.935
  },
  {
    "text": "- Oh boy, oh boy, oh boy!",
    "start": 40.706,
    "duration": 1.102
  },
  {
    "text": "- Okay, Squidward.",
    "start": 41.841,
    "duration": 0.901
  },
  {
    "text": "But if you change your mind,",
    "start": 42.775,
    "duration": 1.402
  },
  {
    "text": "we'll be in this box.",
    "start": 44.21,
    "duration": 1.401
  },
  {
    "text": "- Let's play mountain climbing\nadventure.",
    "start": 45.644,
    "duration": 2.804
  },
  {
    "text": "- Let's go for it!",
    "start": 48.481,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "- Gloves.\n- Check.",
    "start": 50.749,
    "duration": 1.336
  },
  {
    "text": "- Hats.\n- Check.",
    "start": 52.118,
    "duration": 1.368
  },
  {
    "text": "- Underwear.\n- Uh, check.",
    "start": 53.519,
    "duration": 2.303
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Spongebob] Okay, Patrick.",
    "start": 55.855,
    "duration": 0.834
  },
  {
    "text": "Climb up there and secure this\nrope.",
    "start": 56.723,
    "duration": 1.868
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Patrick] You got it.\n(grunting)",
    "start": 58.624,
    "duration": 2.703
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm shaking hands with Neptune!",
    "start": 61.36,
    "duration": 1.169
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoo! Excelsior!",
    "start": 63.729,
    "duration": 2.737
  },
  {
    "text": "- Where's that remote?",
    "start": 66.499,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Patrick] I am the lizard\nking!",
    "start": 67.8,
    "duration": 3.304
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Spongebob] Patrick, Patrick.",
    "start": 71.137,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "Patrick, I think we should\nkeep out voices down!",
    "start": 72.905,
    "duration": 3.237
  },
  {
    "text": "We might start an avalanche!",
    "start": 76.175,
    "duration": 2.202
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Patrick] What?",
    "start": 78.41,
    "duration": 1.201
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Spongebob] I said I think\nwe should keep our voices down!",
    "start": 79.645,
    "duration": 3.17
  },
  {
    "text": "- Will you two shut up?",
    "start": 82.848,
    "duration": 2.37
  },
  {
    "text": "(explosion)",
    "start": 85.251,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "(Spongebob and Patrick yelling)",
    "start": 86.252,
    "duration": 3.971
  },
  {
    "text": "(Spongebob and Patrick sobbing)",
    "start": 96.629,
    "duration": 4.004
  },
  {
    "text": "- Spongebob?",
    "start": 103.936,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "(Spongebob and Patrick yelling)",
    "start": 104.937,
    "duration": 4.738
  },
  {
    "text": "(Spongebob and Patrick sobbing)",
    "start": 109.708,
    "duration": 2.703
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Patrick] Hold me.",
    "start": 112.444,
    "duration": 1.436
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Spongebob] Hang in there,\nbuddy.",
    "start": 113.913,
    "duration": 0.934
  },
  {
    "text": "The chopper's on the way.",
    "start": 114.88,
    "duration": 1.569
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Patrick] Spongebob,\nmy legs are frozen solid.",
    "start": 116.482,
    "duration": 3.103
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll have to cut them off with\na saw.",
    "start": 119.618,
    "duration": 2.27
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Spongebob] No,\nPatrick, I can't do that.",
    "start": 121.921,
    "duration": 1.735
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Patrick] Why not?",
    "start": 123.689,
    "duration": 1.068
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Spongebob] Because I\nalready cut off my own arms.",
    "start": 124.79,
    "duration": 2.57
  },
  {
    "text": "- [Patrick] No!",
    "start": 127.393,
    "duration": 1.202
  },
  {
    "text": "- All right, where it is?",
    "start": 129.495,
    "duration": 1.702
  },
  {
    "text": "- Here I am.\n- Where's what, Squidward?",
    "start": 131.23,
    "duration": 1.969
  },
  {
    "text": "- Don't \"where's what,\nSquidward\" me.",
    "start": 133.232,
    "duration": 2.202
  },
  {
    "text": "Where's the tape recorder?",
    "start": 135.467,
    "duration": 1.202
  },
  {
    "text": "- We don't have a tape\nrecorder, Squidward.",
    "start": 136.702,
    "duration": 1.869
  },
  {
    "text": "- Don't \"we don't have a\ntape recorder, Squidward\" me.",
    "start": 138.604,
    "duration": 3.203
  },
  {
    "text": "- But we don't.",
    "start": 141.84,
    "duration": 1.035
  },
  {
    "text": "- We have a tape recorder box.",
    "start": 142.908,
    "duration": 2.503
  },
  {
    "text": "- All right, make way you two.",
    "start": 145.444,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm coming in.",
    "start": 146.445,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "- Welcome aboard, Squidward!",
    "start": 148.28,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "You've just set sail\non the SS Imagination.",
    "start": 149.848,
    "duration": 3.938
  },
  {
    "text": "Where our only destination\nis fantastic adventure.",
    "start": 156.288,
    "duration": 3.07
  },
  {
    "text": "Where do you want to go first?",
    "start": 159.391,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "- No, no, don't mind me.",
    "start": 160.392,
    "duration": 2.103
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm just here to observe.",
    "start": 162.528,
    "duration": 1.402
  },
  {
    "text": "- But Squidward, don't you see?",
    "start": 163.963,
    "duration": 2.402
  },
  {
    "text": "Waiting and watching?",
    "start": 166.398,
    "duration": 1.836
  },
  {
    "text": "That's not what the box is\nabout.",
    "start": 168.267,
    "duration": 2.169
  },
  {
    "text": "It's about imagination.",
    "start": 170.469,
    "duration": 1.769
  },
  {
    "text": "- All right, fine!",
    "start": 174.473,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "Take me to Robot Pirate Island.",
    "start": 175.674,
    "duration": 1.836
  },
  {
    "text": "I want to arm wrestle\nwith cowboys on the moon.",
    "start": 177.543,
    "duration": 3.07
  },
  {
    "text": "Just do it so I can get back and\nwatch TV.",
    "start": 180.646,
    "duration": 3.671
  },
  {
    "text": "- Okay, Squidward.",
    "start": 184.35,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "Robot Pirate Island it is!",
    "start": 185.718,
    "duration": 2.47
  },
  {
    "text": "- Beep, beep, beep.",
    "start": 189.855,
    "duration": 1.535
  },
  {
    "text": "- Argh.",
    "start": 191.423,
    "duration": 1.269
  },
  {
    "text": "- Boop, boop, boop, boop.",
    "start": 192.725,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "- Ahoy, matey.\n- Beep, beep.",
    "start": 194.393,
    "duration": 2.436
  },
  {
    "text": "- For that, you'll walk the\nplank.",
    "start": 196.862,
    "duration": 2.436
  },
  {
    "text": "(Spongebob and Patrick giggling)",
    "start": 199.331,
    "duration": 3.571
  },
  {
    "text": "(Squidward groaning)",
    "start": 202.935,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "- Why won't this thing turn on?",
    "start": 204.47,
    "duration": 2.47
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, fine.",
    "start": 207.873,
    "duration": 0.935
  },
  {
    "text": "If you don't want to\nshow me, I don't care.",
    "start": 208.841,
    "duration": 2.903
  },
  {
    "text": "I've got better things\nto do than pace the floor",
    "start": 211.777,
    "duration": 3.204
  },
  {
    "text": "wondering how you two work this\nthing.",
    "start": 215.014,
    "duration": 2.436
  },
  {
    "text": "How do those two work that\nthing?",
    "start": 217.483,
    "duration": 1.168
  },
  {
    "text": "There's got to be a secret\nbutton or a switch or something.",
    "start": 218.684,
    "duration": 4.572
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, listen to that.",
    "start": 223.289,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "(metallic clanking)\n(lasers firing)",
    "start": 224.59,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": "Now that sounds like Robot\nPirate Island.",
    "start": 226.058,
    "duration": 2.637
  },
  {
    "text": "Think, Squidward, think.",
    "start": 229.728,
    "duration": 1.536
  },
  {
    "text": "I got it.",
    "start": 231.297,
    "duration": 1.034
  },
  {
    "text": "When those two go to bed,",
    "start": 232.364,
    "duration": 1.402
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll sneak in there and find\nthat button.",
    "start": 233.799,
    "duration": 2.67
  },
  {
    "text": "(crickets chirping)",
    "start": 236.502,
    "duration": 3.003
  },
  {
    "text": "(whimsical orchestral music)",
    "start": 241.573,
    "duration": 3.805
  },
  {
    "text": "It's got to be around here\nsomewhere.",
    "start": 246.845,
    "duration": 1.636
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't see anything.",
    "start": 248.514,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "It's just an empty box.",
    "start": 249.415,
    "duration": 2.102
  },
  {
    "text": "Maybe it really was their\nimagination.",
    "start": 252.417,
    "duration": 2.637
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, get it together, Squidward.",
    "start": 255.087,
    "duration": 2.536
  },
  {
    "text": "What are you saying?",
    "start": 257.656,
    "duration": 1.002
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, do I really believe",
    "start": 258.691,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "that if I sit here and\npretend to drive a race car,",
    "start": 260.359,
    "duration": 3.27
  },
  {
    "text": "that I'm suddenly gonna\nstart hearing noises?",
    "start": 263.662,
    "duration": 2.837
  },
  {
    "text": "What the...\n(engine revving)",
    "start": 267.533,
    "duration": 2.536
  },
  {
    "text": "It actually works!",
    "start": 270.102,
    "duration": 1.802
  },
  {
    "text": "I can't believe it!\n(engine revving)",
    "start": 271.937,
    "duration": 1.969
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh boy, this beats TV by a long\nshot! (laughing maniacally)",
    "start": 273.939,
    "duration": 5.006
  },
  {
    "text": "Whoo! (laughing hysterically)",
    "start": 279.178,
    "duration": 2.769
  },
  {
    "text": "This is the most fun I've ever\nhad!",
    "start": 281.98,
    "duration": 3.004
  },
  {
    "text": "Only two more laps til the\nfinish line. (laughing)",
    "start": 285.017,
    "duration": 3.537
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm in the lead.",
    "start": 288.587,
    "duration": 0.868
  },
  {
    "text": "Out of my way!",
    "start": 289.488,
    "duration": 0.935
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm almost there. (laughing)",
    "start": 290.456,
    "duration": 3.937
  },
  {
    "text": "Victory is mine! (laughing)",
    "start": 294.426,
    "duration": 2.37
  },
  {
    "text": "(Squidward grunting)",
    "start": 296.829,
    "duration": 3.07
  },
  {
    "text": "(Squidward groaning)",
    "start": 301.4,
    "duration": 3.07
  },
  {
    "text": "- Hey, our box is gone!",
    "start": 305.904,
    "duration": 2.036
  },
  {
    "text": "- Oh well.",
    "start": 307.973,
    "duration": 0.768
  },
  {
    "text": "- I know, let's go see\nSquidward.",
    "start": 308.774,
    "duration": 2.136
  },
  {
    "text": "- I hope he's not too\ndown in the dumps today.",
    "start": 310.943,
    "duration": 3.0
  }
]